Mulombodi wa mushindu eu utu ne lutatu lua kuangata mapangadika adi kaayi asankisha bantu, kubapesha dinyoka, kubalumbuluisha, kubapesha majitu, ne kubalomba bua kuandamuna bua bienzedi biabu.
Ku luseke lukuabu, mutontolodi mmuntu udi umona ne: udi ne bua kushintulula tshintu tshionso tshidi tshisumbu tshienza bua tshikale tshiende yeye.
Nansha biobi bikale nanku anyi kabiyi nanku, mulombodi ke udi ne bujitu bua bipeta bimpe anyi bibi bia tshisumbu.
Ngikadilu eu utu misangu ya bungi ufikisha ku ditapulula balombodi ne bantu bakuabu.
Bena mu tusumbu tua muinshi mua buloba batu batumikila mikenji ya dibenga kubuelakana mu malu a tshididi ya muomumue ne ya muinshi mua buloba, kadi kudi dishilangana dikese.
