Dikuatshishangana pankatshi pa masama a buongo ne bikadilu bimpe didi diambuluisha bamanyi mu makebulula abu.
Mbimanyike katshia ku kale ne: tunyinganyinga tua bungi, mputa ne bisama bia mu buongo bitu binyanga bikadilu bia bantu ne bishintulula amue malu adi buongo buenza.
Dilubuluka dia malu a biamu didi dituambuluisha bua kumona ne kukonkonona bitupa bia buongo bituvua katuyi banji kumona.
Ebi bidi bitupetesha malu a bungi ne bintu bia kuenza nabi makebulula bidi bituambuluisha bua kumvua bimpe malu adi mu buongo buetu.
Nansha mudiku dipetangana pankatshi pa meji a biamu ne dimanya dia biamu, meji a biamu adi tshitupa tshinene tshia malu a ordinatere, adi atangila ngikadilu, didisangisha dia malongesha ne meji a biamu.
Makebulula adibu benza bua biamu bidi ne meji adi atangila mushindu wa kuenza biamu bidi bienza midimu idi ilomba meji.
Tshilejilu, udi mua kulombola malu, kulongolola malu ne kualongolola, kuandamuna nkonko ya bantu ne kuandamuna nkonko yabu, kumanya bianza, dîyi ne mpala wa muntu.
Malu aa akalua malongesha a pa buawu avua atangila dikeba dia mandamuna a nkonko minene ya mu nsombelu.
Batu batamba kuenza mudimu ne biamu bia meji a biamu lelu mu malu a mpetu, a manga, a biamu bia mudimu ne a busalayi, bu mudibi mu ordinatere ya ku nzubu ne mu manaya a ku ordinatere.
